title: S6 END....NO SILVER BANER AND NO SUMONER ICON
body: Hi! i have a question because at the end of this seasson i mean s6,i finish ranked mode silver 4 and i expected to get my reward i mean the silver baner and sumoner icon...i know if you were gold or above you get maokai skin....but i was just silver.....but my baner and sumoner icon stil want it:D.....and now the question....this season only gold or above get those staf??? :(

replies.body:
There are some [ongoing issues](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#eune) with certain players not receiving ranked rewards yet. If you reach out in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new), we'll be happy to take care of you.

Let me know if you have any questions.
